Oil, Gas and Consumable Fuels

Company Overview of Delaware City Refining Company LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Delaware City Refining Company LLC operates as an oil refinery. The company processes heavy slate of crudes with a high concentration of high sulfur crudes. It possesses a distribution network of pipelines, barges and tankers, and truck and rail for the distribution of its refined products. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Delaware City, Delaware. Delaware City Refining Company LLC operates as a subsidiary of PBF Holding Company LLC.


4550 Wrangle Hill RoadDelaware City, DE 19706United StatesFounded in 2010



Phone: 302-834-6000

Fax: 302-834-6016








